    icon: 'eye',
    title: 'Structured Visibility',
    description: 'Watch agents work in real time through the Agent Client Protocol. Tool calls, file diffs, permission requests, thinking blocks, and task progress — structured and readable, not raw terminal output.',
  },
  {
    icon: 'shield',
    title: 'Bring Your Own Cloud',
    description: 'Your code runs on your VMs, in your cloud account. Cloud credentials are encrypted per-user with AES-256 — never stored in plaintext anywhere. You control costs, regions, and data residency. Revoke access anytime by rotating your API key.',
